frames.caption: A serene scene unfolds under cherry blossom trees, where a monk stands quietly observing a butterfly fluttering amidst falling petals. The backdrop features a traditional wooden structure, adding to the tranquil atmosphere. Soft sunlight filters through the blossoms, casting a gentle glow over the scene.
frames.description: The scene is set in a peaceful garden with cherry blossom trees in full bloom. A monk is present, standing near a traditional wooden building, while a butterfly flutters through the air, surrounded by drifting petals.

frames.caption: A serene scene unfolds in a tranquil garden where a monk sits in meditation on a moss-covered ground. Cherry blossom petals drift gently in the air, while a white dove takes flight nearby. The warm sunlight filters through the trees, casting a peaceful glow over the traditional wooden structure in the background.
frames.description: The scene is set in a peaceful Japanese garden, featuring a meditative monk, cherry blossoms, and a traditional wooden building. The atmosphere is calm and reflective, enhanced by the gentle movement of petals and the flight of a dove.
